def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return (item + bins) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.sin(np.pi * (item / bins))
```

```python
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return (item + np.sum(bins)) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.log(1 + np.sin(np.pi * item / bins))
```

