    return (item * np.mean(bins)) / (np.std(bins) + 1e-8) + np.sin(np.pi * item / (bins + 1e-8))
```

```python
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return (item * (bins + 1)) / (np.sum(bins) + 1e-8) + np.exp(item - np.mean(bins))
```

